\ell_1 = 0 \quad q_1 = 0 \quad \nu_1 = \lambda \delta_1 \\ \ell_2 = \alpha \Gamma(1-\alpha) \quad q_2 = 0 \quad d\nu_2(y) = \alpha \Gamma(1-\alpha) y^{-\alpha-1} \, dy
